Implement a simple RESTful API using Python. The API should have the following endpoints: 
Before Calling the endpoints
  
   cmd:python manage.py makemigrations
   cmd:python manage.py migrate
   
Then its ready to call endpoints 
ENDPOINTS

GET "/users"          Returns a list of all users.
POST "/users"         Creates a new user with the provided data (e.g., name, email). 
GET "/users/{id}"     Returns the details of a specific user based on their ID.
DELETE "/users/{id}"  Deletes a specific user based on their ID.

